#PokemonGO5YearAnniversary 🎉 In celebration of and appreciation for all the players who have walked, discovered, and changed the world with us, we’ve recollected some of our most memorable moments from over the last five years! 
With the world as our stage, and Pokémon by our side, our journey is never-ending! Join us as the world of Pokémon GO continues into the next phase of our adventure. Let’s GO Trainers!

node.text:
With this year being both the 25th anniversary of Pokémon and the fifth anniversary of Pokémon GO, this year’s Pokémon GO Fest is sure to be a special event! #PokemonGOFest2021

Join us as we go behind the scenes with some Niantics who were there when Pokémon GO launched, and learn what it was like when Pokémon GO changed the world in 2016.
Check out this and other #PokemonGOFest2021-themed video and audio content here: https://pokemongolive.com/post/pokemongofest2021-content

Learn more by visiting the link in our bio.

node.text:
#PokemonGO5YearAnniversary 🎉 In celebration of and appreciation for all the players who have walked, discovered, and changed the world with us, we’ve recollected some of our most memorable moments from over the last five years! 
With the world as our stage, and Pokémon by our side, our journey is never-ending! Join us as the world of Pokémon GO continues into the next phase of our adventure. Let’s GO Trainers!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 13, 2021. May be an anime-style image of text.

node.text:
Ready, set, pose! 📷 

Pokémon GO’s Fashion Week event is back this year with a variety of Pokémon in stylish costumes strutting their stuff! https://pokemongolive.com/post/fashion-week-2021 
#PokemonGOFashionWeek

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 12, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text: Have you figured out how to evolve Inkay yet? Here’s a handy infographic to show you how! Tag a friend who might need this tip!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 10, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Which costumed Pokémon will walk the runway during this year’s Fashion Week event? 

Stay tuned. 👀
#PokemonGOFashionWeek

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 10, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Oh, what’s this? 🙃 

Why, hello there, Malamar! 👋😰
Welcome to Pokémon GO!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'Company NIANTIC PRESENT PokéNoN FEST 2021 SPONSORED - Google Play'.

node.text: Inkay, the Revolving Pokémon, has made its Pokémon GO debut! Complete Field Research tasks for a chance to encounter this Dark- and Psychic-type Pokémon during the Psychic Spectacular event!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text: 👻 Don’t get startled, but October’s #PokemonGOCommunityDay will feature Duskull, the Requiem Pokémon, on October 9! Save the date! https://pokemongolive.com/post/communityday-oct21

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Are you prepared for the Great League Remix? Review the list of ineligible Pokémon to see what you’ll need to prepare for!

#GOBattle

node.text:
Trainers, the Psychic Spectacular event has started in some areas around the world! 🔮 

Psychic-type Pokémon have begun to appear more often in the wild, in raids, and in Field Research encounters! https://pokemongolive.com/post/psychic-spectacular-2021

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 05, 2021. May be a cartoon of ball and text.

node.text:
Remember, Trainers! For a limited-time, you can complete Field Research to earn lots of Poké Balls, Great Balls, and Ultra Balls!

Learn more about the Season of Mischief here: https://pokemongolive.com/post/season-of-mischief-2021

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on September 05, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
Hoopa has arrived in areas around the world! 

For limited-time, certain Pokémon will be appearing in the wild and attracted to Incense! 
Catch them all to complete a limited-time Collection Challenge!
Learn more about the Season of Mischief here: https://pokemongolive.com/post/season-of-mischief-2021

node.text:
The next part of the Season of Mischief Special Research story will be available on September 5! Don’t miss your chance to encounter Hoopa! Plus, Psychic-, Ghost-, and Dark-type Pokémon will be appearing in the wild and attracted to Incense!

Learn more here: https://pokemongolive.com/post/season-of-mischief-2021
